  "title": "Assistant Store Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>WHO WE ARE</strong></p>\n<p>Bed Bath N’ Table is a true family owned business success story.  We are proud of our unique, privately owned family run business that has been operating since 1976 with over 180 stores across New Zealand, Australia and Singapore (and growing!).</p>\n<p><strong>ABOUT THE ROLE</strong></p>\n<p>We are looking for an experienced <strong>Assistant Manager</strong> to join our passionate and talented team at our beautiful store located at <strong>Parkway Parade.</strong></p>\n<p>This is a key role that will see you supporting the Store Manager in developing and coaching the team to deliver that exceptional customer experience and drive outstanding store sales.</p>\n<p>At Bed Bath N’ Table we operate with a minimum of two team members during shifts where possible, to ensure we deliver an exceptional customer experience each and every time.</p>\n<p><strong>THE PERFECT PROFILE</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Ability to sell</li>\n  <li>Previous experience in a fast paced, high volume retail sales environment</li>\n  <li>A passion for homewares and vested interest in Bed Bath N’ Table</li>\n  <li>A drive to achieve monthly sales targets and individual KPI's</li>\n  <li>An eye for detail and high visual merchandising standards</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>BED BATH N' TABLE WILL OFFER YOU:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Health Benefits</li>\n  <li>Staff discounts of 30% off full price products and an additional 15% off reduced items to keep your home looking beautiful</li>\n  <li>Rewards available for referring amazing new talent to join the team</li>\n  <li>Career progression and development</li>\n  <li>To be part of a stable and growing business</li>\n</ul>",
