    "description": "<p>As a premium homewares and lifestyle company, it is our desire to bring you quality products that will enhance the enjoyment of your home. We aim to bring the wonderfully rich pattern and colour of the world around us into all of our designs and products. As a global company, we scour the world (be it Portugal, Turkey, China or Vietnam) searching for the most beautiful qualities to incorporate into everything we create.</p>\n<p>Our brand reflects our love of the land we call home, bringing the beauty of the modern Australian lifestyle to you. As an ever-expanding team, it is our continuous goal to make life in your home a pleasure.</p>",
